text: Viktoriya Gorodchanina (born 9 November 1987) is an Uzbekistani female water polo player. She was a member of the Uzbekistan women's national water polo team. She was a part of the team at the 2009 World Aquatics Championships. == References == ==Other websites == * Uzbekistan Viktoriya Gorodchanina (R) vies with Hungarian Dora Kisteleki during the water-polo group A game getty Category:1987 births Category:Living people Category:Uzbekistani water polo players
